{"type": "article", "id": 9231, "title": "传统屏风灯具", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-06T06:52:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234938cS3oQRVBJfvYZXLK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tLambert &amp; Fils 推出了一款以中国传统屏风为设计灵感的灯具。灯管被放置在矩形的框架中，其中，框架选用黑色钢材，而连接关节处则使用了黄铜，其排列方式看起来像极了传统的屏风。这款灯有悬挂式和站立款式两种选择，将会参加 2015 年 5 月 16 至 19 日的纽约国际当代家具展。这是<a href=\"http://www.lambertetfils.com/\" target=\"_blank\">工作室的官方主页</a>，可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052349342TUdgLure3nqG0Ki.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234934zLl4KGCoJPEwOaXu.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234935VPH72nsgzjNaFfY9.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234935bQEuq5sYIrc93OAl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234936gPWDnLx9HJGQFNcV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234936TEMYcdxKyJpjuH7O.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234937JwXm7YlP9yVgGx0k.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67395833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}